data.meta_description: In MEMORY of ESTHER ROLLE on her BIRTHDAY - American actress best known for her role as Florida Evans, on the CBS television sitcom Maude, for two seasons (1972–1974), and its spin-off series Good Times, for five seasons (1974–77, 1978–79), for which Rolle was nominated for a Golden Globe Award for Best Actress - Television Series Musical or Comedy in 1976.    Nov 8, 1920 - Nov 17, 1998   (complications of diabetes)
